{
  "id": "adv_event_2411_01_05_01",
  "title": "最強の\nニコイチ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』まで　あと5日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――5 days left until the “Hoshimi Friend Festival”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.8999999523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "ワンツーワンツー……はぁ……うまくいかない……\nなんでkanaさんはあんな綺麗にステップ踏めるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One-twoー one-twoー… haa… Not going well…\nHow can kana-san step so clearly?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "endTime": 13.7726301193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ここはもっと大きく動かないとkanaさんと並んだ時\n見栄えが悪いし……あー難しい！　もう一回！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to move bigger here‚ otherwise it won't look good\nwhen I'm next to kana-san… Ahー difficult! Once more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9666666667,
      "endTime": 23.1565535228,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9400.0157692
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "そこ、無理に大きく動こうとしなくていいよ\nそれより止めを意識して。後はkanaが合わせるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you don't have to move too much there\nInstead‚ focus on the finish. kana will get the timing right later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3666666667,
      "endTime": 30.8433787028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん！？　どうしてここに……？\n今日はこころ達のレッスンお休みですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san!? Why are you here…?\nWe don’t have a lesson today‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0333333333,
      "endTime": 37.095623810999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "……まさかまさかですけど\nもしかしてkanaさんも自主練です……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I can't believe it‚ but\nAre you here for some self-practice too‚ kana…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3,
      "endTime": 43.5298639298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "んな訳ないでしょ。忘れ物取りに来ただけ\nほんと星見のやつらって自主練好きだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. I just come to get something I forgot\nHoshimi Girls really love self-practice",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6333333333,
      "endTime": 52.1322017033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ですよね～。kanaさんが自主練なんてしたら\n空から焼きそばの雨が降ってきますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess so~. if kana-san ever did self-practice‚\nit'd be raining yakisoba from the sky~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3333353679,
      "endTime": 59.429548517899995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　軽口叩く暇あるなら練習しろ！\n本番で無様なパフォーマンスしたら許さないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? If you have time to joke‚ focus on!\nI won't forgive you if you perform poorly during the real stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6333353679,
      "endTime": 66.7068045299,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_break-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7199.997965400002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃぃぃっ！　だから角を引っ張らないで下さい～\n痛いです、怖いです、悪魔です～～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehhh! So don't pull on my horns~\nIt hurts‚ it's scary‚ you're devil~~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.8333333333,
      "endTime": 74.0162130673,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14899.99999999999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ただ踊るだけじゃなくもっと要所でファンサ意識！\nあと、サビ前のフリはもう少し大きく！　じゃあね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't just dance‚ but more conscious of fan service at key points!\nAlso‚ make the dance moves before the chorus a little bigger! See you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.2,
      "endTime": 82.03333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』　当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the “Hoshimi Friend Festival”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6333312989,
      "endTime": 84.9933298111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.9933298111
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.5000009786
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9333384197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "そこ、間違ってる\n意味的にto不定詞じゃなくて動名詞でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That part's wrong\nSemantically‚ it's a gerund‚ not a to-infinitive",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9333384197,
      "endTime": 93.69150168110001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんがこころちゃんの英語の宿題を\n見てあげてる……？　それも仲良く肩を並べて……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san is helping Kokoro-chan with her\nEnglish homework…? And they're standing side by side…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9000050863,
      "endTime": 101.391456159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ！　凄い！　kanaちゃん英語得意なんだ！？\n芽衣も教えてもらいたいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow! Amazing! kana-chan's good at English!?\nMei want to learn too~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6000050863,
      "endTime": 108.5515696843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.766671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "驚くのはそこじゃない気が……！\nでも、二人が仲良くなって良かった……一安心",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't think that's not surprising point…!\nAnyway‚ I'm glad two of them got along well… I'm relieved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.766671753,
      "endTime": 116.21356525430001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.4000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "なかなか手ごわいライバルになりそうだなぁ\nでも、優勝するのは芽衣達だよ！　負けないもん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're going to be a pretty tough rival\nBut‚ the winner is Mei's unit! We won't lose!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4000050863,
      "endTime": 124.5452657065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.7333384197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "こんな状態で明日の小テスト大丈夫なの？\n優勝したらすぐに取材あるし勉強時間取れないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this situation‚ is tomorrow's note test okay?\nIf you win‚ you'll have an interview right away and won't have time to study",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7333384197,
      "endTime": 133.25746523549998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.466671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないじゃないですか～……\n今週は仕事忙しくて全然学校行けなかったんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because there is no other way~…\nI've been busy with work this week and haven't been able to go to school",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.466671753,
      "endTime": 140.2916604043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.5000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "せめてどこが出そうとかヤマ張れないの？\n授業ノート見れば大体分かるっしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't you at least make a guess where it will come out?\nIf you look at your class notes‚ you'll have a pretty good idea",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5000050863,
      "endTime": 146.5795513472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.766671753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "あー、こころちゃん学校に友達いないもんね～\n貸してくれる子なんていないか。ごめんねぇ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahー‚ Kokoro-chan‚ you don't have any friends at school~\nNo one's going to lend you theirs. Sorry~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.766671753,
      "endTime": 155.1085990906,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12377.93467329999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.3000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ～、それがですね。じゃーん、見て下さい！\n実はあるんですよ～、お休みした日の授業ノートが！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufufu~‚ here it is. Ta-da‚ take a look!\nI actually have them~‚ the class notes from the days I had a break!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3000050863,
      "endTime": 166.2249030431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.1446064263
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.4333384197
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2411_01_05-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "やるじゃん！　その根性は認めるけど……\nさすがに学校で盗みはしちゃダメだよ？　警察行こ",
      "translations": {
